== Japanese ==
=== Etymology ===
English, タイム (time) + アタック (attack), but not used to indicate a playthough of a game's dedicated mode for achieving fast completions ([[time attack]]), as one would expect; instead, it is the dominant terminology for both unassisted [[speedrun]]s and [[tool-assisted speedrun]]s in [[Japan]] (there is no commonly used [[loanword]] deriving from the term “speedrun”).

